            <h3>What is CLI-izdat?</h3>
            <p>CLI-izdat is a system of visual communication developed from the ongoing study of the aesthetic and technological relationships between Eastern Bloc samizdat practices, command-line interfaces, and early diskmag subculture.</p>
            <p>Visual and text references are collected in the <a href="https://www.are.na/aleg-lutz/cli-izdat" target="_blank">are.na channel</a> of the same name.</p>
